ZH: 我每年都会去农村度假，享受田园生活。
EN: I go on vacation to the countryside every year to enjoy the rural life.

ZH: 在田园中，你可以看到美丽的田野、绿油油的牧场和迷人的花坛。
EN: In the countryside, you can see beautiful fields, lush pastures, and charming flower beds.

ZH: 孩子们在田园里奔跑、玩耍，自由自在地度过每一天。
EN: Children run and play freely in the countryside, enjoying each day.

ZH: 田园风光让我感到如此宁静和放松，远离都市的喧嚣。
EN: The rural scenery makes me feel so calm and relaxed, away from the hustle and bustle of the city.

ZH: 这座小村庄被翠绿的山脉和广阔的田野所环绕。
EN: This small village is surrounded by lush mountains and vast fields.

ZH: 我曾经在一个田园农场里体验了种植蔬菜的乐趣。
EN: I once experienced the joy of growing vegetables in a rural farm.

ZH: 我希望有一天能拥有一座自己的田园别墅，远离尘嚣。
EN: I hope to one day own my own rural villa, away from the noise and pollution.

ZH: 在田园里，你可以呼吸到清新的空气，感受大自然的气息。
EN: In the countryside, you can breathe in the fresh air and feel the touch of nature.

ZH: 田园生活简单而宁静，人们注重互助合作和自然的循环。
EN: Rural life is simple and peaceful, with a focus on mutual help and natural cycles.

ZH: 这个小村庄有一座古老的田园风格的庙宇，吸引了许多游客来参观。
EN: This small village has an ancient temple with a rural style, attracting many tourists to visit.

ZH: 我试图在城市中重现一些田园风格的元素，以缓解压力和疲劳。
EN: I try to recreate some elements of rural style in the city to relieve stress and fatigue.

ZH: 为了追求田园生活，我决定放弃高薪的工作，搬到乡下种田。
EN: In pursuit of a rural life, I decided to give up a high-paying job and move to the countryside for farming.

ZH: 我特意设计了一个田园风格的花园，种植各种花草树木。
EN: I deliberately designed a garden with a rural style, planting various flowers, plants, and trees.

ZH: 在田园里，你可以看到农民们勤劳耕种的身影，他们为我们提供食物。
EN: In the countryside, you can see the hardworking farmers cultivating the land, providing us with food.

ZH: 乡村里的人们生活简单，但却过得很幸福和满足。
EN: People in the countryside live a simple life, but they are happy and content.

ZH: 这座美丽的田园小镇每年吸引着许多人来度假和体验农耕。
EN: This beautiful rural town attracts many people every year for vacation and experiencing farming.

ZH: 她的梦想是有一个纯朴的家园，拥有自己的田园菜园。
EN: Her dream is to have a simple home with her own vegetable garden.

ZH: 我喜欢在田园里散步，欣赏大自然的美景和宁静。
EN: I enjoy taking walks in the countryside, appreciating the beauty of nature and the tranquility.

ZH: 在田园中的一所小屋里，我度过了一个宁静而难忘的假期。
EN: I spent a peaceful and unforgettable vacation in a cottage in the countryside.

ZH: 这个村庄的居民都过着宜人的田园生活，很少受到城市的纷扰。
EN: The residents of this village live a pleasant rural life, rarely affected by the hustle and bustle of the city.
